A Nigerian politician and entrepreneur, Oloye Akin Alabi, reacted to a tweet on his verified Twitter account about an hour ago that he will support Tinubu even if he was a Labour Party member.
One of the beauties of democracy is that everyone has the right to make a choice; choice of presidential candidate, choice of political party etc.
However, A Twitter user by the name ” Idoreyin14″ tweeted Oloye Alabi that ” With Due respect sir, Party aside, Can you let Tinubu run your Family affairs? If you weren’t in APC, would you gladly vote for Tinubu….?
Oloye Alabi reacted to the tweet and said he can let Alhaji Bola Ahmed Tinubu, the All Progressive Congress(APC) presidential candidate, run his life. He added that he will even beg him to run it.
Akin Alabi said that should prove beyond a doubt and be enough to show how much he believed in the presidential candidacy and in the person of Tinubu. He added that even if he was a member of the Labour Party, he would still support Tinubu.
Oloye Akin Alabi’s tweet,
“I can let Tinubu run my life. I will even beg him to run it. Shows how much I believe in him. Even if I was a member of the Labour Party, I would still support him.”


